comments: [Observable in enhanced video] Sexton (CLE) lifts his pivot foot before releasing his dribble.
Brunson (DAL) legally contests Love's (CLE) shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) and Love (CLE) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Zizic (CLE) sets the screen in Harris's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (DAL) makes marginal contact with Stauskas's (CLE) arm after he releases the pass.
Nowitzki (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Zizic (CLE) in the post.
Nowitzki (DAL) extends his arms into Sexton's (CLE) back while setting the pick and delivers contact that affects his ability to maintain his defensive position.
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Nowitzki's (DAL) arm after he releases his shot attempt and does not affect his follow-through.
Powell (DAL) grabs and pulls Love (CLE) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Stauskas (CLE) wraps Kleber (DAL) as he disengages from the pick and affects his SQBR.
Zizic (CLE) has his forearm rested on Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) body during his shot attempt, but does not extend it into him to deliver contact that would affect the shot attempt.
Harris (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Sexton (CLE).
Harris (DAL) grabs Nowitzki's (DAL) jersey and pulls him into Sexton's (CLE) path while setting the screen. Nowitzki delivers contact that affects Sexton's ability to defend the play.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Harris (DAL).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) legally contests Stauskas's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
